de.ityx.mediatrix.api.client

Interface ICPTME


  • public interface ICPTME
    Provides functions to manage ptme module. The text objects can be suggested for a mail dependent of the mail content. The operator mustn't search for them but select from suggestion panel left in the customer history tree.
    How to use:
    API.getClientAPI().getPTMEEngineAPI().getPTMEEmail(emailid);
